  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses security at drinking water facilities.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>requires a community water system to: <hr><ltbullet1>complete a security plan; and<hr><ltbullet1>report a security breach to the Utah Cyber Center within two hours of discovering the security breach;<hr><ltbullet>requires the Division of Drinking Water to report annually to two legislative committees on security at community water systems;<hr><ltbullet>classifies a community water system's security plan as a protected record; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
